window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Continue the best-selling series!</p> <p>The LitRPG with heart continues towards its epic conclusion...</p> <p>Time is running out, and the most ambitious adventurers in the world are coming after Harvey and his friends. Harvey, Reacher, and Tabitha have all been touched by the Eldritch and gained incredible new abilities as a result. But at what cost?</p> <p>As word reaches them of plots to capture Harvey and kill Felodin, the odds dramatically shift against the friends as the fate of the world hangs in the balance.</p> <p>Father of Constructs is a Gaslamp/Steampunkish series set in an apocalyptic world.</p>"; 
